	n="37"/>kuśalī| śrī-puṇḍravarddhana-bhuktau koṭīvarṣa-viṣaye halāvartta-maṇḍale kṛta-hala-kula-pramāṇena triśatiko<choice><sic>pe</sic><corr>tpa</corr></choice>ttau vudhavaḍā-khā¦<lb 
