	n="40"/>ṇḍapāśika-śaunakika-kṣetrapa-prāntapāla-koṭapāla-Aṅgarakṣa-tad-āyuktaka-viniyuktaka-hastyaśvanau<supplied reason="omitted">vala</supplied>v<choice><sic>ṛ</sic><corr>yā</corr></choice>pṛtaka-kiśoravaḍa<lb 
