	n="50"/>-muraripurātadevaśarmmaṇe māghe māsi paurṇṇamāsyā<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> manvantarādau gaṅgāyām vidhivat<supplied reason="omitted">·</supplied> snātvā vṛhad-rāja-śrī-kumāra<lb 
