	n="52"/>sanī-kṛtya pradatto smābhiḥ| Ato bhavadbhiḥ sarvvair evānumantavyaṁ*| bhāvibhir api bhūpatibhiḥ bhūmer dāna-phala-gauravāT Apahara<lb 
